| Strategy              | What customer sees                      | What mechanic does            |
| --------------------- | --------------------------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| `diagnostic_only`     | “Inspection first, no guessing”         | Confirms issue before quoting |
| `range_quote`         | “Estimated range depending on findings” | Explains best/worst case      |
| `fixed_simple`        | “Clear price”                           | Low-risk services             |
| `inspection_required` | “Needs on-site assessment”              | Prevents unsafe quoting       |
