5️⃣ How This Appears in the UI
Customer (simple)
Issue: Car won’t start
ℹ️ Most issues like this require a quick diagnosis before repair.
✔ No guessing
✔ Price explained before work

Mechanic (smart)
Likely Systems: Battery / Starter
Required Skills: Electrical, Diagnostics
Suggested Quote: Diagnostic
Risk: Medium
